            <pb n="1R"/>
            <p rend="align(center)">
                <addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee>
                <placeName>Pa.</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="align(center)">Dear Sir</p>
            <p><sic>You</sic> favor came duly to hand<lb/> &amp; duly attended to<lb/> The freight
                for the books<lb/> will be paid, as soon as the<lb/> amount due to you for the<lb/>
                book will be sent the freight<lb/> will be included</p>
            <p>We had yesterday a great day<lb/> here, the new <sic>jewish</sic> hospi˶<lb/>tal was
                dedicated, <persName>Wise</persName><lb/> declined to be present <persName>Dr.
                    Lili</persName>,<lb/>put <sic>Spoke</sic> and exalted the<lb/> prosperity of
                Religion in<lb/>
                <placeName>Israel</placeName> which becomes daily more<lb/> and more the connection
                of the<lb/> heart, for benevolence is the<lb/> only true Religion which<lb/> all the
                Prophets and sages</p>
            <pb n="1V"/>
            <p>alluded to when <sic>the</sic> repre˶<lb/>manded the people for their<lb/>
                irreligious life.</p>
            <p>My <sic>Speech</sic> which I delivered<lb/> at the occasion I shall<lb/> send you as
                soon as it<lb/> will copied</p>
            <p>Hoping that these lines<lb/> will find you enjoying<lb/> the best health<lb/> I
                remain Sir most<lb/> Respectfully<lb/> Yours</p>
            <p>
                <persName role="author">Dr <add>?</add></persName>
            </p>
        </body>
